### Winetricks for Hidden Expedition Titanic ###
- Game doesn't save "Play in Window setting"
- Fulscreen doesn't scale properly making mouse position off
# Need to set Winetricks (via Proton Tricks>default prefix>change settings):
vd=800x600 (enable virtual desktop, set size to 800 x 600)
winxp
# to match 800x600 fixed resolution of this game and Win XP compatibility
# 
# Can clean up Desktop that shows by deleting links in C:\users\<user>\Desktop
# Can set a wallpaper for a splash screen (or black for blank) with 
"HKCU\Control Panel\Desktop" 
    key: Wallpaper
    Value: C:\wallpaper.jpg
    
    
